package name :

the package name is consist of : package-name. pk-version .miror pk version.commpataple releas(el9).noarch.rpm


the deffrince between version and miror pk version : 


-in version we can find a large change in that pk but in miror


[noarch : to determin the arch of processor is any arch  ]

-----------------------------------------------

# if we have the rpm file of an app downloaded we dont need to use yum to install it

[ we can install it by command : rpm -i rpm-file-path ]



- to show the progress in installing rpm use option -v

- to show the percentage in hash use option -h

[ command: rpm -ivh rppm-file-path ]

-----------------------------------------------

# to list all pk installed 

[ rpm --query --all : rpm -qa ]



[root@redhat ~]# rpm -qa
